context.arch.intelligibility.presenters
Class StringPresenter

java.lang.Object
  context.arch.intelligibility.presenters.Presenter<java.lang.String>
      context.arch.intelligibility.presenters.StringPresenter
Direct Known Subclasses:
ConsoleStringPresenter
public class StringPresenter
extends Presenter<java.lang.String>

A basic Presenter that renders Explanation based on its content DNF. If renders each explanation as a String. It only handles the content Expression based on whether it is a DNF, Reason or Parameter.

See Also:
Presenter, Explanation, Expression, DNF, Enactor
